@article{10.1145/3732801.3732837,
	abstract = {Under the wave of digital intelligence, artificial intelligence drives the reform in the field of education, and the process of digital transformation of education is accelerated. This paper focuses on the teaching reform of ai-enabled sports training course in the era of digital intelligence. Analyze the integration trend of artificial intelligence and sports training science, build a solid theoretical foundation from educational technology and learning science, and clarify the integration mechanism and adaptation. It innovates the teaching mode of sports training course driven by artificial intelligence, and constructs the three-drive collaborative intelligent teaching mode, personalized learning mode and collaborative intelligent learning mode. To explore the teaching practice path of enabling sports training course with intelligent teaching assistant, intelligent student aid, intelligent assistant management and intelligent assistant evaluation. Pointed out that the artificial intelligence can face the traditional teaching mode, data security privacy, teachers role transformation difficulties, technology application challenges, and put forward to update the teaching idea, strengthen data security management, improve teachers artificial intelligence literacy, optimize technology application environment strategy, for sports training courses with the help of artificial intelligence to improve teaching quality, realize innovation and development to provide a comprehensive theory and practice reference.},
